data.description: *****Seller is offering buyers agent incentive (Bonus) of $2,500 with a reasonable and accepted offer. *****Welcome to his Captivating Horse Ranch Estate!! Immerse yourself in the idyllic charm of this exceptional 10-acre estate, nestled at the end of a picturesque tree-lined driveway. Here, the beauty of the countryside takes center stage, enveloping you in a serene and enchanting atmosphere.  Welcome to a captivatingjust outside of Rose Hill offers a 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom home, thoughtfully designed across 2,922 square feet to seamlessly blend with the natural splendor that surrounds it. Step into a welcoming haven, enhanced by a wood-burning fireplace that radiates warmth and comfort.  Safety and security are paramount, and a robust concrete safe room ensures peace of mind in any situation.  Venture into the expansive 40x50 barn/building, currently transformed into the ultimate game-watching man cave. Designed with meticulous attention to detail, this versatile space boasts an epoxy floor, industrial-grade garage doors, a full bathroom, and washer/dryer hookups - offering a seamless blend of functionality and comfort.  As you explore the outdoors, you're met with an inviting covered porch that overlooks the 18x36 pool, a true oasis for relaxation. Elevating your leisure and entertainment experience, discover a 12x20 pool house and a covered outdoor entertainment area. Plus, a screened-in 14 x 14 Tiki bar invites you to enjoy the outdoors while being shielded from the elements. Escape to your very own countryside haven, where the symphony of nature and luxury creates an enchanting retreat. Embrace a lifestyle that seamlessly combines tranquility and refinement - schedule a tour today!
